The paper proposes a method for automatic multi-organ segmentation in DECT using a 3D FCN, which is a popular technique in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The application of the method is in biomedical research and clinical settings, which falls under the category of medical imaging (cs.MED) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
